queries.sql: SELECT `file`, `kegiatan_csr`.`id`, `kegiatan_csr`.`tahun`, `ruang_lingkup`.`ket` as `ruang_lingkup`, `urusan_bidang`.`ket` as `urusan_bidang`, `urusan_bidang`.`id` as `id_urusan`, `kegiatan_csr`.`program_kegiatan`, `aktifitas`, `kegiatan_csr`.`alamat`, `kalurahan`.`nm_kapanewon` as `kapanewon`, `kalurahan`.`id_kapanewon` as `id_kapanewon`, `kalurahan`.`nm_kalurahan` as `kalurahan`, `kalurahan`.`id_kalurahan` as `id_kalurahan`, `kegiatan_csr`.`biaya`, `kegiatan_csr`.`volume`, `kegiatan_csr`.`satuan`, `kegiatan_csr`.`opd`, `nama_perusahaan`, `waktu`, `nominal` FROM `kegiatan_csr` JOIN `detail_kegiatan_csr` ON `kegiatan_csr`.`id`=`detail_kegiatan_csr`.`id_kegiatan_csr` JOIN `user` ON `detail_kegiatan_csr`.`id_user`=`user`.`id` JOIN `perusahaan` ON `user`.`id`=`perusahaan`.`id_user` JOIN `ruang_lingkup` ON `kegiatan_csr`.`ruang_lingkup`=`ruang_lingkup`.`id` JOIN `urusan_bidang` ON `kegiatan_csr`.`urusan_bidang`=`urusan_bidang`.`id` JOIN `kalurahan` ON `kegiatan_csr`.`kalurahan`=`kalurahan`.`id_kalurahan` WHERE `file` is NOT NULL
